spec_data.Name: perl-Data-JavaScript
spec_data.Description:
This module is mainly intended for CGI programming, when a perl script
generates a page with client side JavaScript code that needs access to
structures created on the server.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:25:50 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Dump perl data structures into JavaScript code
